data.description: Check out this stunning home featuring numerous upgrades, an expansive backyard situated on a pristine preserve lot, and no CDD fees! The focal point of this home is the gourmet kitchen, complete with a spacious pantry. The generously sized living room provides a captivating view of the vast backyard and a covered patio. There's also a formal dining room for family gatherings. The first-floor master suite boasts two dual vanities for added convenience. On the second floor, you'll discover a sizable flex/media room, a walk-in storage closet, four bedrooms, a jack-n-jill bathroom, and an additional third bathroom. The convenience of upstairs laundry is a definite plus. Recent gutter installations enhance the property. it's conveniently located near Oakleaf Town center!
